qsopcast is a GUI front-end of the Linux command line executive of P2P network TV.

Library requirements:
qt4

Compilation and install: go to the src subdirectory and execute the following commands:
$mkdir build
$cd build
$cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=relwithdeb ..
$make
$make install

Usage:
you need to setup these following files before using qsopcast
Linux version command line executive sp-sc from http://www.sopcast.com
Linux version command line executive xpplive from midlinux repo
Linux version ppstream libraries from http://www.ppstream.com
Linux version command line executive xpps compiled from sources from qsopcast

Language support:
Currently Several other languages are supported besides English. To use one of them, make sure your environmental variable LANG is configured properly.
